{"tid":2025973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方反對支聯會本月底舉行六四遊行","createTime":"2020-05-20T15:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T15:40:16.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2470d29e2f93df5aecbfa8a011f663988400e5b7","tid":2025973,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方反對支聯會在本月31日舉行六四遊行。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會申請在本月31日下午3時至5時，由灣仔修頓球場出發遊行去中聯辦外，並分別在起點及終點舉行集會。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，法例禁止任何公眾地方進行多於八人的群組聚集，有關遊行和集會不屬於獲豁免的群組，而本港就新型冠狀病毒的應變級別仍維持「緊急」的最高級別，相信有關活動，會增加參與者及市民大眾感染病毒的風險，因此反對支聯會的遊行，並禁止他們集會。支聯會表明會上訴。"},{"pid":"fd964af001a47ce2d12e73ce976c9fe758992b34","tid":2025973,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=391695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391695&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=4b650752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391695&h=2c8f89d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=391695</a>"},{"pid":"3a09b2ccd22b4d68ead764ffe5e278186b145433","tid":2025973,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347b3074cbfc75e25d7e0e5551a677e732dd5061","tid":2025973,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"係咪史上第一次反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"d0bbcdc08af20c650d59c1608872bb6574a2b521","tid":2025973,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"347b3074cbfc75e25d7e0e5551a677e732dd5061","tid":2025973,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"係咪史上第一次反對<i